author: ekoneil
msg: Reorganize the WSM tests.  This breaks the tests into standalone JUnit tests and tests that require a running Axis server.  The source directories are organized as:
junit-services -- web services used in standalone JUnit tests.  This directory can be merged with the junit/ directory when the WSM annotation processor works off of Mirror rather than reflection.
junit-server -- tests that execute against Axis running in a server
The webapp/ directory still contains the wsmWeb project which now has significantly fewer files in WEB-INF/src.
